      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Greenvale%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "A sign marks the Greenvale Train Station for the Long Island Railroad, a reminder of the town’s rail heritage.",
